{"tid":2216861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共稱「學員全結業」被揭講大話  新疆增建IV級制集中營","createTime":"2020-09-25T04:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T02:40:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":50,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"69a51a5eece149c719da04641927883219633182","tid":2216861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200925/33IMG4XQ2NFKBKUNGOBZEZ43TU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200925%2F33IMG4XQ2NFKBKUNGOBZEZ43TU%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=86118ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200925%2F33IMG4XQ2NFKBKUNGOBZEZ43TU%2F&h=1a41461c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200925/33IMG4XQ2NFKBKUNGOBZEZ43TU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中共稱「學員全結業」被揭講大話 <br />\n新疆增建IV級制集中營<br />\n<br />\n中國政府在去年12月曾稱新疆「培訓學員已全部結業」，不過說法被揭不實。澳洲戰略政策研究所（ASPI）公佈「新疆數據計劃」研究結果，發現在去年12月後，新疆至少61座已存在的監禁設施動工建造新的設施。參與製作這份報告的澳洲新疆議題專家雷國俊（James Leibold）稱，希望數據庫能夠說服全球各國對中國政府採取更多反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：扣反華帽子 北京禁兩澳學者入境<br />\n<br />\n根據「新疆數據計劃」研究，自2017年起統計出超過381座拘留營，數字比對上一次調查，至少多了100座。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ajlsEeFkTypheIlzoHixdyELrxg=/2102x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TXNJINFR5NEJPDFDM2GD674L2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FajlsEeFkTypheIlzoHixdyELrxg%3D%2F2102x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTXNJINFR5NEJPDFDM2GD674L2I.jpg&h=395cde06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■研究指出中國說謊，去年底至今仍不斷增建新疆集中營。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳研究所公開數據冀國際施援<br />\n<br />\n第二級大多用來關押維吾爾人與其他少數民族，約有94座，入面有教室，多與工廠及倉庫相連，相信亦與外界指摘的「強迫勞動」有關。研究認為此類仍然是中共希望「再教育」維吾爾人多於永久拘留。<br />\n<br />\n第三級是中高級保安拘留中心，約有72座，相信是拘留一些情節嚴重的維吾爾族人。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n主導研究計劃的研究員魯瑟 （Nathan Ruser）稱，中國政府一直指「再教育營」已不存在，但今次研究顯示新疆政府在2019年與2020年仍持續投資建造新的監禁設施。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雷國俊透露，ASPI希望透過今次資料庫，令之前被關押的維吾爾人，認出再教育營的確切地點，令他們的證詞更具體可信。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建「喝酒培訓基地」逼破戒<br />\n<br />\n此外，飲酒在伊斯蘭教法當中是不允許的，但網上流傳新疆一處餐廳被改作喝酒培訓基地，海外穆斯林稱中國當局想藉此滅絕少數民族文化。。。。。。。。。。。中國外交部發言人汪文斌回應指，新疆事務純屬內政，所謂「強迫勞動」問題完全是西方機構和人員憑空揑造的謊言。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲戰略政策研究所<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C3UXm-weEjoEroqQlSdZ9yYV1HU=/686x812/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TJPRRCOVIFENTDELBCWDF23OXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC3UXm-weEjoEroqQlSdZ9yYV1HU%3D%2F686x812%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTJPRRCOVIFENTDELBCWDF23OXA.jpg&h=550ce9a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cc03ac5ead9b7728b51f0f53b114b9eb320f2a1","tid":2216861,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"無人推?<br />\n我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ffb82a234d642d0f94ae5f33f6676925741d39","tid":2216861,"uid":237555,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"真係好驚香港有一日會變咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbb41c33dea04709f39f94086e5b93039bf2989","tid":2216861,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"11ffb82a234d642d0f94ae5f33f6676925741d39","tid":2216861,"uid":237555,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"真係好驚香港有一日會變咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r